commit.title: [numeral] [plugins] Switch from `Big_int` to ZArith.
commit.message:
[numeral] [plugins] Switch from `Big_int` to ZArith.

We replace Coq's use of `Big_int` and `num` by the ZArith OCaml
library which is the supported option these days.

This PR is still work in progress.
